220
00:12:55,675 --> 00:12:57,975
I hope you'd hurry and get out of here.

221
00:12:59,175 --> 00:13:00,875
From my Japan.

222
00:13:01,975 --> 00:13:04,274
That conviction of his!

223
00:13:04,275 --> 00:13:05,474
"Zero" is a code name meaning,

224
