242
00:14:01,275 --> 00:14:03,275
But, what on earth could it be?

243
00:14:09,075 --> 00:14:11,274
I give up, Amuro.

244
00:14:11,275 --> 00:14:12,774
Tell me won't you?

245
00:14:12,775 --> 00:14:15,774
