255
00:14:35,975 --> 00:14:39,174
and yet has a flower circle and a score of 100 on it.

256
00:14:39,175 --> 00:14:41,174
Don't you think it's strange?

257
00:14:41,175 --> 00:14:43,774
True.

258
00:14:43,775 --> 00:14:45,274
Wait a second.

259
00:14:45,275 --> 00:14:46,374
Hold it...

